    <id>earmark</id>
    <name>Earmark</name>
    <summary>Self-hosted scrobble store</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[Record what you listen to, on a server you control. Earmark is a lightweight self-hosted scrobble store: it accepts scrobbles from Last.fm-compatible clients, imports your full Last.fm and Spotify history, resolves listens to MusicBrainz, and shows your listening stats — all inside Nextcloud, with none of the heavy infrastructure a full ListenBrainz needs.]]></description>
